Yeiri said.
   Firestone's board of directors recommended that shareholders
accept Bridgestone's offer to purchase Firestone's 32 million
outstanding shares for $80 a share. Bridgestone was spurred to make
the $2.6 billion offer Thursday because of an unsolicited offer
from Italian tiremaker Pirelli SpA.
